They said that they were holding my family for ransom and that I’ll need to give them 69420 dollars, then a group of people with a Donald Trump mask broke into my house and tied me down. They knocked me out for what felt like countless hours. They brought me to a basement and then I saw all my family sitting down, unconscious on what looked like a satanic ritual. Than the people with the Donald Trump face mask came waving their arms around. They then circled the circle and began chanting “BUILD A WALL” I was scared for my life and then they pulled out their Yu-Gi-Oh Fusion Card. They fused and became the man himself, Donald .J Trump. Donald then proceeded to cut my leg off and that made be go unconscious. I then woke up in my bed thinking it was a dream but for some reason one of my legs was smaller than the other one. I got a text on my phone and it was Donald Trump. The text said that he only gave me half of my family. I then checked up on my family and was horrified. They were all laying down but EACH ONE OF THEIR HALVES ARE MISSInG😡. I guess it was true he did give me half of them. But I saw that my sisters leg was not there. I suddenly realized that I HAVE MY SISTERS LEG. I was horrified. I then got a text that told me to go in the attic, I went and saw a box. I opened it up and their were adoption papers FOR ME. I read hem and realized that I was given to my parents at the age of three. Than I realized something. If I was adopted ThAT MeANS ThAt I HavE A sTRangers LeG. After that uninstalled the Trump app but it was too late all of the deep web knew my address  and sent hit men and assassins after me. I then jumped out of my window and became a new person. I legally changed my name and then became a better person. And that’s the story of how I become The amazing Spider Man of today. 😘
